snippet.title: Dread X Collection 5 Game Spotlight #1
snippet.description:
A glimpse at 6 of the 12 games for the upcoming Dread X Collection 5. 


Featuring: 
VisceralError – Rotten Sigma
Conner Rush of FYRE Games – We Never Left
Shakles – Gallerie
Darkstone Digital –The Book of Blood
colorfiction – Resver
iwilliams  – Ludomalica

Wishlist on steam now:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1899810/Dread_X_Collection_5/
